wikipedia_page.main: Mary Anne "Marian" Belcher (12 March 1849 – 15 December 1898) was an English educator and school administrator, the second headmistress of Bedford High School.

response: * Marian Belcher (1849–1898) became headmistress of Bedford High School.
Thomas Belcher's sister Marian Belcher (1849-1898) was headmistress at Bedford High School.
